short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A cross-listing extension for furniture sellers. Developed by Kashew.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Download this extension to allow Newish.ai to cross-list your products on your Chairish account.

The extension will grant permission to post on your account.
